oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Bart Gordon in departmental library
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Bart Gordon was born and educated in Rutherford County, attended MTSU, and graduated in 1971. He then received his law degree from the University of Tennessee in 1973. Notes on the back of the photo indicate this photo was used in the Midlander yearbook.
